graph TB
    subgraph "Client Layer"
        CLI[CLI Client<br/>- Encrypt/decrypt locally<br/>- Sign commits<br/>- Merge conflicts]
        WebUI[Web Browser<br/>- Email auth<br/>- Team management<br/>- Audit reports]
        CICD[CI/CD Pipeline<br/>- Scoped API tokens<br/>- Branch allow-lists]
    end

    subgraph "Cloudflare Edge"
        Edge[DNS + TLS<br/>WAF / Rate Limiting<br/>Turnstile]
        Access[Cloudflare Access<br/>Internal and staging apps]
        APIShield[API Shield<br/>Schema validation / optional mTLS]
    end

    subgraph "Cloudflare Workers Platform"
        AppWorker[Dashboard + API Worker<br/>Static Assets + Hono<br/>OpenAPI contracts]
        QueueWorkers[Queue Consumers<br/>Email retries<br/>Audit fanout<br/>GitHub sync<br/>Envelope checks]
        RotationWF[Workflows<br/>Rotation saga<br/>Checkpointed retries]
        BranchDO[Durable Objects<br/>Branch write serialization<br/>Single-use tokens<br/>Rate counters]
        KV[Workers KV<br/>Read-mostly config cache]
    end

    subgraph "SSH Data Plane"
        Tunnel[Cloudflare Tunnel / Spectrum<br/>TCP edge for SSH]
        SSH[Go SSH Gateway<br/>- Authenticate SSH keys<br/>- Authorize commands<br/>- Push / pull / share<br/>- Issue bridge tokens]
    end

    subgraph "State Layer"
        Hyperdrive[Hyperdrive<br/>Postgres connection pooling]
        PG[(Managed Postgres<br/>- Identity/auth<br/>- RBAC relations<br/>- Branch policies<br/>- Crypto metadata<br/>- Commits/branches<br/>- Audit events)]
        R2[(Cloudflare R2<br/>Encrypted snapshots only<br/>Log exports)]
    end

    subgraph "Security Material"
        Secrets[Cloudflare Secrets Store<br/>Provider credentials<br/>Non-secret-data signing keys]
    end

    subgraph "Trust Boundaries"
        TB1[Trusted: User device + private keys]
        TB2[Semi-trusted: Server control plane]
        TB3[Untrusted: Network + storage dumps]
    end

    WebUI -->|HTTPS| Edge
    CICD -->|HTTPS bearer token| Edge
    CLI -->|SSH| Tunnel

    Edge --> AppWorker
    Edge -.-> Access
    Edge -.-> APIShield
    Tunnel --> SSH

    AppWorker --> BranchDO
    AppWorker --> Hyperdrive
    AppWorker --> R2
    AppWorker --> KV
    AppWorker --> QueueWorkers
    AppWorker --> RotationWF
    QueueWorkers --> Hyperdrive
    QueueWorkers --> R2
    RotationWF --> BranchDO
    RotationWF --> Hyperdrive
    RotationWF --> R2

    SSH --> BranchDO
    SSH --> Hyperdrive
    SSH --> R2
    SSH --> AppWorker

    Hyperdrive --> PG
    AppWorker -.-> Secrets
    QueueWorkers -.-> Secrets
    RotationWF -.-> Secrets

    CLI -.->|Plaintext exists only here| TB1
    AppWorker -.->|Metadata only| TB2
    SSH -.->|Metadata + ciphertext only| TB2
    R2 -.->|Ciphertext objects| TB3
    PG -.->|No plaintext secrets| TB3

    subgraph "Branch Access Control"
        B1[1. Validate identity]
        B2[2. Check org/team membership]
        B3[3. Check repo permission]
        B4[4. Match branch policy]
        B5[5. Serialize branch update in Durable Object]
        B6[6. Persist audit and branch state]

        B1 --> B2 --> B3 --> B4 --> B5 --> B6
    end

    AppWorker -.->|Evaluates| B1
    SSH -.->|Evaluates| B1

    subgraph ".wenvy/ Local Directory"
        LC[config.json<br/>head.json<br/>branches/<br/>envelopes/<br/>snapshots/<br/>keys/<br/>logs/]
    end

    CLI -.->|Maintains| LC

    classDef trusted fill:#90EE90
    classDef semiTrusted fill:#FFD700
    classDef untrusted fill:#FFB6C1
    classDef encrypted fill:#87CEEB

    class TB1 trusted
    class TB2 semiTrusted
    class TB3 untrusted
    class R2 encrypted
